A timeseries 
========================================================

&nbsp;

```{r, echo=FALSE, warning=FALSE, message=FALSE}
library(forecast)
library(dplyr)
library(ggplot2)
library(readr)
library(ggfortify)
library(tidyr)
```


```{r, echo=FALSE}
df <- read_csv("monthly-sales-of-tasty-cola.csv", col_names = c("month", "sales"), skip = 1,
               col_types = cols(month = col_date("%y-%m")))
ggplot(df, aes(x = month, y = sales)) + geom_line() + ggtitle("Monthly sales of Tasty Cola")
```


