Sometimes we may compare several timeseries.
========================================================

&nbsp;

```{r, echo=FALSE}
df <- read_csv("deaths-from-homicides-and-suicid.csv", col_names = c("year", "homicide", "suicide"), skip = 1)
df <- gather(df, key = 'type', value = 'deaths', homicide:suicide)
ggplot(df, aes(x = year, y = deaths, color = type)) + geom_line() + scale_colour_manual(values=c("green","blue")) +
  ggtitle("Australia: Homicides and suicides")
```


